room_title: Escape room "The Paris Heist" by Escapades in Sioux Falls
room_address: 3313 S Western Ave Sioux Falls, SD 57105
room_description: Your team is made up of hotel workers who work at the Paris hotel that houses Kim K.'s apartment. You notice that sometimes she leaves her apartment not wearing her ring. Now you have carefully planned a robbery. You have 60 mins to find her ring and disarm her security and get out!
